{
  "stem": "1061.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, as a matter of fact, other children did join because it made it more interesting.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The group that I was with, there were four of us, you see?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She actually took my friends, you see, so that, first of all, it created a wonderful atmosphere, and there was the old competition, you see?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I-- it might not be nice to say-- sounds like bragging-- but I was very, very good student in-- in my childhood and after.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But anyhow, I loved school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I absolutely adored school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never had enough of it, you see?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that these children were more or less on my level, and the old competitive spirit was there, you see?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they-- they were actual lessons with homework, with-- you know, divided into units of-- of-- you know, this is for a year, for this year, for fifth year, for sixth year, whichever.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It made it extremely interesting, really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I personally, speaking of that, with a neighbor's boy who was my friend-- he was not in my class-- we decided to open a library, a lending library.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] He reminds me of it all the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I see him once a year when I'm in New York when we meet for the yahrzeit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, once a year, my hometown survivors meet in New York to-- for the-- for the anniversary of the liquidation of town.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he-- he lives in Connecticut.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He comes in-- [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mitye. ?] And he always reminds me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, remember when he opened the library?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We really opened the lending library.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the kids who were not attending, quote unquote 'my class,' you see, we had a little stand, and we had books, and we wrote out cards.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
